# PRACTICAL 4: DATA ANALYTICS I
# Linear Regression using Boston Housing Dataset
#
# Dataset:
# Download train.csv from:
# https://www.kaggle.com/c/boston-housing/data
#
# Target Column: medv
# Objective:
# Predict house prices using Linear Regression.
